Summary: Object appeared in picture of clouds
divs: Sighting DetailsTook a picture of pretty clouds to the west of me. I was in the car, window down. Snapped with my Iphone quickly before traffic obscured my view. Looked at photo and cannot explain object. No bugs or birds in the area. Object was not seen with naked eye.
